      • findReservationById

        Optional<ReservationEntity> findReservationById​(Long id)
        Finds reservation by id
        Parameters:
        id - the identifier, a number which uniquely identifies a reservation
        Returns:
        If reservation with this id was found, return Optional with non-null value. Then value will be ReservationEntity object. Otherwise return empty Optional object.
